snippet.title: Cro-Mag Rally XBLIG Gameplay
snippet.description:
Cro-Mag Rally XBLIG Gameplay

"Cro-Mag Rally is the wildest kart racing game since man invented the wheel! You are a speed-hungry caveman named Brog who races through the Stone, Bronze, and Iron Ages in primitive vehicles with plenty of weapons to fend off your opponents!"

Created by: citizen12 studio

Price: 240 MSP

Download link: http://marketplace.xbox.com/en-US/Product/Cro-Mag-Rally/66acd000-77fe-1000-9115-d80258550a4c?DownloadType=GameDemo#LiveZone


Follow me at: http://twitter.com/RealAJWalker
